shirk","tag-manners-adab","tag-patience-sabr","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-prophetic-biography-seerah-nabawiyya","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-unbelief-kufr","tag-war-al-harb"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6be","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":6555,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/umar-converts-to-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":23760,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Umar: The Prophet prays for Umar&#8217;s conversion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, strengthen Islam with one of two men whom you love more: Abu Jahl or Umar ibn al-Khattab.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cThe most beloved of the two was Umar.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3681 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37215,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/25\/sahaba-bayat-al-shajarah-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23760,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hudaybiyyah: All who pledged under the tree in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone of the companions who pledged allegiance under the tree will enter Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3860 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u0627\u064e \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062d\u064e\u062f\u064c\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/22\/allahs-kalam-best\/","url_meta":{"origin":23760,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Allah\u2019s words better than all other speech","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe superiority of the words of Allah over all other words is like the superiority of Allah over His creation.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2926 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6290,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/12\/prophet-loves-makkah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23760,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Makkah: The Prophet loves his hometown of Mecca","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn 'Adi reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while he was standing near Mecca and saying, \u201cBy Allah, you are the best and most beloved land to Allah. Had I not been driven away from you, I would not have left you.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37874,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/afiyah-ask-allah-wellness\/","url_meta":{"origin":23760,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on \u2018Afiyah: Ask Allah for wellness in this life and next","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-\u2018Abbas reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, teach me something to ask Allah Almighty.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAsk Allah for wellness.\u201d I waited for some days, then I came back, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, teach me something.\u201d The Prophet said to me,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41292,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/ummah-majority-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23760,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Muhammad\u2019s nation a majority in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people of Paradise are lined up in one hundred and twenty rows. Eighty of them are from this nation, and forty are from the rest of the nations.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2546 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23760","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=23760"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23760\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=23760"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=23760"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=23760"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}